'''Marisa Sartika Maladewi''', born June 28, 1993 in [[Yogyakarta]],<ref name=unsri/> is an [[Indonesia]]n beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned [[Puteri Indonesia 2013]] 1st Runner-up <ref>[http://missosology.org/more/uncategorized/item/1731-puteri-indonesia-2012-2013-live-updates Whulandary Herman is Puteri Indonesia 2012-2013]</ref> and represented her country at the [[Miss International 2013]] pageant.

==Personal life==
Marisa is a student agribusiness at [[Sriwijaya University]].

==Pageantry==

===Puteri Indonesia 2012-2013===
Marisa competed as the representative of [[South Sumatera]]. She won the title [[Puteri Indonesia 2013|Puteri Indonesia Lingkungan 2013]] or the 1st Runner-up title.<ref>[http://www.waspada.co.id/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=277594:keluarga-marisa-sartika-maladewi-terharu-harumkan-sumsel&catid=77:fokusutama&Itemid=131 Keluarga Marisa Sartika Maladewi terharu harumkan SUMSEL]</ref>

===Miss International 2013===
As the 1st Runner-up of Puteri Indonesia 2013, Marisa represented [[Indonesia]] at the Miss International 2013. But she failed at the pageant.

