r=SAGE |year=2009 |ISBN=1-4129-5085-6}} *{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=lJBiJTKt5n8C&printsec=frontcover |title=Criminological Perspectives on Race and Crime |author=Shaun L. Gabbidon |publisher=Taylor & Francis |year=2010 |ISBN=0-415-87424-6}} *{{cite book |title=A Theory of African American Offending: Race, Racism, and Crime |author1=James D. Unnever |author2=Shaun L. Gabbidon |publisher=Taylor and Francis |year=2011 |ISBN=0-415-88358-X}}
